    title: 'Building resilience through \'Open Source Seed Systems\' for climate change adaptation in Kenya, Uganda, and Tanzania: What are the options for policy?',
    summary: 'This policy brief presents recommendations for establishing Open Source Seed Systems (OSSS) in Kenya, Uganda, and Tanzania to enhance climate resilience and food security. It addresses the gap between formal seed systems that serve only 20% of farmers\' needs and farmer-managed seed systems that lack policy support, proposing policy reforms to enable free access, use, and exchange of plant genetic materials.',
