    what_it_does: 'The review uses Diffusion of Innovations (DOI) theory as a reference framework to analyze MSD programs and identify factors that contribute to behavior change scale-up. It synthesizes literature to develop a six-domain model covering Design, Perceptions, Business Model, Relationships, Communications, and Capacity.',
