    title: 'Gender issues in livestock production in Ethiopia: A review of literature to identify potential entry points for gender responsive research and development',
    summary: 'This is a comprehensive literature review that synthesizes existing research on gender issues in livestock production in Ethiopia, identifying key gender dynamics, constraints, and opportunities. The review analyzes 28 publications to document gender division of labor, access to resources, decision-making patterns, and institutional barriers affecting women\'s participation in livestock value chains.',
